headline: Fastenal Releases 2025 Environmental, Social, and Governance (ESG) Report
summary: WINONA, Minn., July 09, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq: FAST) ('Fastenal', 'we', 'our', or 'us') is proud to announce the publication of our 2025 ESG Report. The report, which covers the year ending December 31, 2024, was produced with reference to the Global Reporting Initiative (GRI) standards and aligns with the ESG disclosure and reporting frameworks established by the Sustainability Accounting Standards Board (SASB, now part of the IFRS Foundation) and the Task Force on Climate-Related Fina
